title: KY-kei JC Kuuki-chan
synopsis: On the first day as a transfer student, Betao comes to meet one girl. Her name is... Kuuki Yominashi! (Her initials "KY" mean "being unable to read the situation/mood.") When Betao with glasses and Kuuki with skippers meet with each other, the gears of fate starts to spin.
staff: [['Ootsuka, Masahiko', ['Producer']], ['Geso, Ikuo', ['Director', ' Character Design', ' Animation Director']], ['Tatemoto, Itsuki', ['Script']]]
